---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ArticleBanner from '../../components/ArticleBanner.astro';
---

<Layout title="Struktur Organisasi Universitas STEKOM - Universitas STEKOM">
    <ArticleBanner title="Struktur Organisasi Universitas STEKOM" breadcrumb="Struktur Organisasi" />

    <!-- Header Section -->
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">
            Struktur <span class="text-cyan-600">Organisasi</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="w-24 h-1.5 bg-cyan-500 mx-auto mb-8 rounded-full shadow-sm"></div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            Hierarki kepemimpinan dan tata kelola institusi Universitas STEKOM yang dirancang untuk efektivitas layanan
            pendidikan.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-16 space-y-16">

        <!-- Struktur Image Display -->
        <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <div
                class="group relative bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 transition-all duration-300">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-transparent to-black/5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity pointer-events-none">
                </div>

                <div class="relative p-2 md:p-4 text-center">
                    <img src="/img/sidbar/stekom.jpg" alt="Struktur Organisasi Universitas STEKOM"
                        class="w-full h-auto object-contain rounded-2xl mx-auto"
                        onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/1200x800?text=Struktur+Organisasi+Universitas+STEKOM'">
                </div>

                <!-- Hover Info (Optional for interactive feel) -->
                <div class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 md:bottom-6 md:right-6">
                    <a href="/img/sidbar/stekom.jpg" download="struktur-organisasi-stekom.png"
                        class="flex items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-4 py-2 md:px-6 md:py-3 rounded-lg md:rounded-xl shadow-xl transition-all hover:scale-105 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400 focus:outline-none">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5"
                                d="M4 16v1a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" />
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-xs md:text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide">Simpan</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Description Section -->
        <section class="relative bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mr-20 -mt-20 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-50 rounded-full opacity-50 filter blur-3xl">
            </div>

            <div class="relative px-8 py-12 md:px-16 md:py-16">
                <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
                        <span class="p-2 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg text-blue-600">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
                            </svg>
                        </span>
                        Tata Kelola Organisasi
                    </h2>
                    <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600 mx-auto max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
                        <p>
                            Struktur organisasi Universitas STEKOM dirancang secara strategis untuk mendukung visi dan misi
                            institusi dalam mencapai standar pendidikan global. Dengan pembagian tanggung jawab yang jelas,
                            setiap unit dapat berkolaborasi secara sinergis.
                        </p>
                        <p class="mt-4">
                            Hierarki ini memastikan proses pengambilan keputusan yang cepat, akuntabel, dan transparan demi
                            memberikan layanan pendidikan terbaik serta pengembangan program studi yang relevan dengan
                            kebutuhan industri masa kini.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </div>
</Layout>
